  <entry>
    <title>单调栈与单调队列</title>
    <url>/2023/01/07/%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%83%E6%A0%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="单调栈"><a href="#单调栈" class="headerlink" title="单调栈"></a>单调栈</h2><h2 id="分类"><a href="#分类" class="headerlink" title="分类"></a>分类</h2><p>单调栈分为单调递增栈和单调递减栈。<br>单调递增栈：从栈底到栈顶递增，栈顶大<br>单调递减栈：从栈底到栈顶递减，栈顶小</p>
<h2 id="功能"><a href="#功能" class="headerlink" title="功能"></a>功能</h2><p>找到当前数左边和右边离自己最近的最大的&#x2F;最小的数。<br>查找比当前元素大的：底部比当前元素大-&gt;单调递减栈<br>查找比当前元素小的: 底部比当前元素小-&gt;单调递增栈</p>
<h2 id="基本模板"><a href="#基本模板" class="headerlink" title="基本模板"></a>基本模板</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">stack = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="built_in">id</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums)):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> stack <span class="keyword">and</span> nums[stack[-<span class="number">1</span>]] &lt; nums[<span class="built_in">id</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">        tmp = stack.pop()</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    stack.append(<span class="built_in">id</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="两种情况"><a href="#两种情况" class="headerlink" title="两种情况"></a>两种情况</h2><ol>
<li><p>数组中没有重复值<br>单调栈中只放下标，假如是单调递增栈。将比它小的元素弹出，只要某个数据弹出，信息开始生成。弹出的元素左边比它大的最近的是栈中它的下一个数，右边比它大的最近的就是当前数。(谁让你弹出的那个数)</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">findNearstMax</span>(<span class="params">nums</span>):</span><br><span class="line">   stack = []</span><br><span class="line">   ans = [[-<span class="number">1</span>]*(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums))]</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">for</span> idx <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums)):</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">while</span> stack <span class="keyword">and</span> nums[stack[-<span class="number">1</span>]] &lt; nums[idx]:</span><br><span class="line">         index = stack.pop()</span><br><span class="line">         ans[idx][<span class="number">0</span>] = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="keyword">if</span> stack <span class="keyword">else</span> -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">         ans[index][<span class="number">1</span>] = idx</span><br><span class="line">     stack.append(idx)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment"># 循环结束后，栈非空，将栈中元素依次出栈</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">while</span> stack:</span><br><span class="line">     idx = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>]  <span class="comment"># 先获得栈顶元素</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment"># 如果栈为空，说明左边没有比它大的</span></span><br><span class="line">     stack.pop()</span><br><span class="line">     ans[idx][<span class="number">0</span>] = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="keyword">if</span> stack <span class="keyword">else</span> -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">     ans[idx][<span class="number">1</span>] = -<span class="number">1</span>  <span class="comment"># 右边没有比它大的</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">return</span> ans</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>数组中有重复值</p>
<p>栈中每个元素生成一个小链表<br>5 4 3 4 5 3 5 6<br>当一个元素出栈时，下面那个链表中最后一个位置，就是左边离它最近的比它大的数。把相同的值下标压到一个链表中。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">findNearstMax</span>(<span class="params">nums</span>):</span><br><span class="line">   stack = []</span><br><span class="line">   ans = [[-<span class="number">1</span>]*(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums))]</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">for</span> idx <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(nums)):</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">while</span> stack <span class="keyword">and</span> nums[stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>]] &lt; nums[i]:</span><br><span class="line">         indexArray = stack.pop()  <span class="comment"># 出栈的是有相同元素的</span></span><br><span class="line">         leftIndex = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="keyword">if</span> stack <span class="keyword">else</span> -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> indexArray:</span><br><span class="line">             ans[i][<span class="number">0</span>] = leftIndex</span><br><span class="line">             ans[i][<span class="number">1</span>] = idx</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> stack <span class="keyword">and</span> stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>] == nums[idx]:</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment"># 如果当前栈不为空且栈顶元素等于当前元素</span></span><br><span class="line">         stack[-<span class="number">1</span>].append(i)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">         stack.append([i])</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">while</span> stack:  <span class="comment"># 栈中还有元素未出</span></span><br><span class="line">      indexArray = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">      stack.pop()</span><br><span class="line">      leftIndex = stack[-<span class="number">1</span>][-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="keyword">if</span> stack <span class="keyword">else</span> -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span> indexArray:</span><br><span class="line">          ans[i][<span class="number">0</span>] = leftIndex</span><br><span class="line">          ans[i][<span class="number">1</span>] = -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> ans</span><br><span class="line">      </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="单调队列"><a href="#单调队列" class="headerlink" title="单调队列"></a>单调队列</h1><p>涉及到滑动窗口，主要用来解决数组中所有长度为k的区间最值问题。<br>当队头下标和当前元素下标-k相等时，说明此时需要移动L</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 所有区间长度为k的最大值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">monotonousQueue</span>(<span class="params">nums, k</span>):</span><br><span class="line">  res = []  <span class="comment"># 存放窗口的最大值</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">help</span> = []  <span class="comment"># 这个队列中队头元素永远是最大的</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> i, value <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(nums):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="built_in">help</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> nums[<span class="built_in">help</span>[-<span class="number">1</span>]] &lt;= value:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment"># 如果队列不为空且队尾元素小于当前元素，则出队</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">help</span>.pop()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">help</span>.append(i)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># L动</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i - k == <span class="built_in">help</span>[<span class="number">0</span>]: <span class="comment"># 队头元素</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">help</span>.pop(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i &gt;= k-<span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment"># 每超过一次L，统计一次</span></span><br><span class="line">      res.append(nums[<span class="built_in">help</span>[<span class="number">0</span>]])</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> res</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
